## StrictExclude type

Strict version of Exclude.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export type StrictExclude<T, U extends T> = Exclude<T, U>
```

## Example


```ts
type Foo = 'a' | 'b' | 'c'
// Expect: 'b' | 'c'
type Bar = StrictExclude<Foo, 'a'>
```
